model

Class Relation

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Relation

  • public class Relation
extends java.lang.Object
    Description of the Relation class
    Contains the data about a given relation. Contains a reference to the solution of the relation. Contains a reference to a sign, if this relation results in a sign.
    Author:
    Watnuss
